<module>
    <h>mi</h>
    <p><g>mi</g>
        <en>I, me</en> is the first person singular <a href="?xx=nouns/personal_pronouns">personal
            pronoun</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-sbj">
            <h>subject</h>
            <p><g>mi</g> can be used as the subject of a verb.</p>
            <p>Examples with <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a>
                <en>be</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>mi</m> trang.</gd>
                        <tr>I am busy.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with other verbs – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Chunnaic <m>mi</m> cù aig an dorus.</gd>
                        <tr>I saw a dog at the door.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>


